      "rationale": "Experimental conditions from the Morrison et al. (2016) hemolysis dataset were fully documented. Fluid temperature, hematocrit, rotational speed, and volumetric flow rates were reproduced in the CFD boundary conditions within 3.1% mean deviation. Traceability to calibrated measurement instruments was confirmed."
