      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH is the primary regulatory metric for CPB device submissions. The CFD-derived RH is computed using the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model integrated along Lagrangian particle trajectories, directly corresponding to the experimental RH measurement protocol. QoI relevance is high."
