      "rationale": "MRL 2 does not require formal use error assessment beyond confirmation that the simulation was performed by a qualified analyst. The lead analyst holds a doctoral degree in computational fluid dynamics with 8 years of cardiovascular simulation experience. No additional use error assessment is required."
    },
