      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form selection justified with reference to literature and sensitivity analysis for the hemolysis constitutive model.",
      "rationale": "The k-ω SST turbulence model was selected based on its established performance for rotating machinery internal flows in published literature. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model was chosen for consistency with regulatory precedent. Sensitivity to turbulence model selection was assessed by comparing k-ω SST and k-ε realizable results; differences in predicted RH were below 8% across the primary operating range."
    },
